0.Title: Nurse midwife
0.Description: A San Antonio-based certified nurse midwife with experience offering care in hospitals, at home, in birth centers as well as clinics, Nikki has helped usher many a child into this world. You can see many of those adorable babies on her Instagram page, which is also filled with some of the breathtaking deliveries she’s done, conversations about vaginal birth after cesarean, and encouragement for moms at all stages.
